    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《风屿奇航》是一部由小说改编的第一人称视角沙盒生存类角色扮演游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与好友们一起踏上冒险旅程 - 在浮空岛舰上建造基地、采集资源并制作各种物件，掠夺战利品，穿梭于云端，体验战斗快感，逐步揭开这个世界的神秘面纱！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/32ca15002de5756e154a06d95008dbec.webp?t=1772116286\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/3cfd011d15d44f889d88813e0c07b900.poster.avif?t=1772116286\" width=616 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/3cfd011d15d44f889d88813e0c07b900.webm?t=1772116286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>踏上冒险之旅！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一手持剑，一手持盾，全副武装加入战斗。在地下城中战斗，消灭各种拦路的敌人，尽情搜刮丰富的宝藏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>施展神秘力量！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用一系列强大的魔法法杖，对付各种极具挑战性的敌人，或者通过炼金术为你的好友提供支援！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/ba9119694d1418a223d0e3633cd839d6.webp?t=1772116286\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/675aef00ff5ac837aded21894be1d6f6.poster.avif?t=1772116286\" width=616 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/675aef00ff5ac837aded21894be1d6f6.webm?t=1772116286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的岛屿 - 你的飞船 - 你的家园！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >登上你的飞船——这座堡垒不仅是你的安全避风港，也是你开启冒险之旅的门户。这不仅仅是一艘飞船——它是你的空中家园，你可以在此制作各种必要的物品，为你的冒险旅程提供助力。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/1e4da23cf0bde42b9113fb02df11b222.webp?t=1772116286\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/589edf7b4401cf63f9ba71e76ce664bc.poster.avif?t=1772116286\" width=616 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/589edf7b4401cf63f9ba71e76ce664bc.webm?t=1772116286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>人多力量大！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与你的好友一起探索《风屿奇航》的无尽世界！本游戏全面支持联机合作和多人游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造个性化的角色！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调节脸部特征，并根据喜好选择各种酷炫的发型和肤色！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/864886c7399f433e2e7edb289f2fd40c.webp?t=1772116286\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/da31c4e0a487709c9add7e85a9a0fdae.poster.avif?t=1772116286\" width=616 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/da31c4e0a487709c9add7e85a9a0fdae.webm?t=1772116286\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索无尽的地平线！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夺取巨大的浮空岛，在天海交汇之际的广阔区域尽情冒险；每一处地平线都能带来新的冒险旅程和各种未解之谜。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在可肆意破坏的环境中塑造专属世界！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验随心所欲自由塑造世界的快感，畅享各种可肆意破坏的环境。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扬帆起航，驶向无垠的天空！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一望无际的地平线启航，直上云霄，开始一段异乎寻常的奇妙旅程！</p>",
